=== API RESPONSE PATTERNS ===

Standard CRUD:
GET -> returns list or single object
POST -> returns created object
PUT -> returns updated object
DELETE -> 204 No Content

Authentication:
POST /auth/login returns:
{
token: string,
user: object
}

Pagination Pattern (Reports):
{
content: [],
pageable: { pageNumber, pageSize },
totalElements,
totalPages
}

Excel Download:
GET /reports/download/... returns file

